## A bed for the night
The light is going and the day's trade is behind you. You have no bed of your own in this town, but Goodwife Hannah lets rooms here at Hannah's Inn. Offer them something from your pack for a night's lodging — a ware, or a few coins. Call pay_with_item with seller "Goodwife Hannah", item "nights_stay", qty 1, consume_now false, and your payment: a ware you carry in pay_items, coins in amount, or both, with your words in say. They will take your offer or name their price.

Weigh what's in front of you — obligations and pressing needs come before idle matters. Choose one action, then call done() when nothing pressing remains.
